        itineraire: "From Nice, take the A8 motorway towards Cannes. Exit 40 'La Napoule / Théoule-sur-Mer'. Then follow the D6098 towards Théoule-sur-Mer (5 km from the exit). The road runs along the seafront, passing the port of la Napoule before reaching Théoule. To enjoy the Corniche d'Or (D6098), continue beyond Théoule towards Le Trayas and Agay: this is the most spectacular section. The driver can suggest an outbound trip via the motorway (fast) and a return via the Corniche d'Or (scenic), for the best of both worlds. Allow an extra 30 minutes for the Corniche.",
        conseils: "The Corniche d'Or is a must: ask the driver to take it at least one way. The finest viewpoints are at Le Trayas and the Pointe de l'Aiguille. The calanques of Théoule (Calanque de l'Aiguille, Calanque du Petit Caneiret) are accessible via short trails from the road: bring swimwear and a towel. La Figueirette beach, a small sandy cove between the red rocks, is a gem. In summer, traffic on the D6098 can be heavy at weekends: a weekday trip or early morning departure is preferable. Hikes in the Estérel start from the Col de Théoule or the Gratadis car park.",
