        comparaisonTransport: "Bus 69 (Ligne d'Azur) connects Nice to Falicon in about 25 minutes for €1.50, but frequency is limited, especially at weekends (a few services per day). The bus serves the main road below the village, which means a walk uphill. By taxi, the 15-minute journey drops you in the heart of the village, effortlessly, and allows you to descend at your chosen time — a considerable advantage when buses are scarce.",
